           SHORT="A tool to read SMART information from harddisks"
cat << EOF
S.M.A.R.T. status checking tool for IDE hard disk drives
ide-smart performs various non-destructive tests on a SMART
(Self-Monitoring, Analysis and Reporting Technology) capable IDE device.

SMART provides near future failure prediction by monitoring different
attributes (listed as IDs) of the device. Your BIOS and hardware need
to support SMART to use this package.
EOF
